General Assembly House Joint
Resolution No. 72
February Session, 2026 LCO No. 3239
Referred to Committee on JUDICIARY
Introduced by:
REP. STAFSTROM, 129th Dist.
SEN. WINFIELD, 10th Dist.
RESOLUTION CONFIRMING THE NOMINATION OF CAMPBELL
BARRETT, ESQUIRE, OF DURHAM TO BE A JUDGE OF THE
SUPERIOR COURT.
Resolved by this Assembly:
1 That the nomination by His Excellency, the Governor, of Campbell
2 Barrett, Esquire, of Durham to be a Judge of the Superior Court, to serve
3 for a term of eight years from the date of confirmation by both Houses,
4 in succession to the Honorable Michael P. Kamp, is approved and
5 confirmed, and he is appointed a Judge of the Superior Court for said
6 term.
LCO No. 3239 1 of 1

